title: Google\Cloud\BigQuery\Migration\V2\ListMigrationSubtasksRequest
name: ListMigrationSubtasksRequest
description:
A request to list previously created migration subtasks.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.bigquery.migration.v2.ListMigrationSubtasksRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The migration task of the subtasks to list. Example: projects/123/locations/us/workflows/1234

params.name: data.read_mask
params.description: Optional. The list of fields to be retrieved.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of migration tasks to return. The service may return fewer than this number.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A page token, received from previous ListMigrationSubtasks call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to ListMigrationSubtasks must match the call that provided the page token.

params.name: data.filter
params.description: Optional. The filter to apply. This can be used to get the subtasks of a specific tasks in a workflow, e.g. migration_task = "ab012" where "ab012" is the task ID (not the name in the named map).
